  "abilities": [
    {
      "name": "Waaagh!",
      "description": "If your Army Faction is ORKS, once per battle, at the start of your Command phase, you can call a Waaagh!. If you do, until the start of your next Command phase, the Waaagh! is active for your army and:\n\n• Units from your army with this ability are eligible to declare a charge in a turn in which they Advanced.\n• Add 1 to the Strength and Attacks characteristics of melee weapons equipped by models from your army with this ability.\n• Models from your army with this ability have a 5+ invulnerable save.",
